Package com.opengamma.strata.product

Interface SecurityQuantityTrade

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CalculationTarget, PortfolioItem, SecurityQuantity, Trade
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ResolvableSecurityTrade, SecuritizedProductTrade<P>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BillTrade, BondFutureOptionTrade, BondFutureTrade, CapitalIndexedBondTrade, DsfTrade, EtdFutureTrade, EtdOptionTrade, FixedCouponBondTrade, GenericSecurityTrade, IborFutureOptionTrade, IborFutureTrade, OvernightFutureTrade, SecurityTrade
    public interface SecurityQuantityTrade
extends Trade, SecurityQuantity
    A trade that is based on security, quantity and price.

    If the trade is directly based on a securitized product, the trade type is SecuritizedProductTrade. If not, the financial instrument involved in the trade is represented in alternative form, e.g., Security. See individual implementations for more details.
